cu.explanation_en: Setting the integrity algorithm to the unknown enum 'nia9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the hardware log level to an invalid value 'invalid' will cause the logging system to fail initialization for hardware components and prevent proper system startup.
du.explanation_zh: 將硬體日誌級別設定為無效值 'invalid' 會導致硬體組件日誌系統初始化失敗，並阻止正確的系統啟動。
